text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Whoa!? A rare monster figure is up for sale!?

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: Hmm, it's so cute! I can't let this chance slip away...!!

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: ...Phew. I ended up clicking 'buy.' My wallet took a huge hit because of it...

text_block_list.name: Matikanetannhauser
text_block_list.text: I'll have to hold off on snacks for a while. And no more buying treats to eat on the go in the shopping district...
And so, Matikanetannhauser unintentionally succeeded in her diet.
